---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="w-[95%] mx-auto max-w-270 flex justify-center rounded-4xl flex-col my-8 bg-[#354eaf] shadow-2xl text-[#faf9f5] px-20 pt-17.5 pb-12.5 max-sm:px-10 max-sm:pt-8.25 gap-8 max-sm:gap-3"
  >
    <h1 class="text-[2.6rem] max-sm:text-[2rem] font-[bungee]">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text text-[1.75rem] max-sm:text-[1.5rem] my-4 font-[bungee] ml-2">
      Effective Date: [Insert Date]
    </p>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to [Your Company Name]. Your privacy is important to us. This
        Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard
        your information when you visit our website [Insert Website URL].
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Data:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, etc.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Non-Personal Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cookies and Tracking Data:</strong> To enhance user experience
          and gather analytics.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>3. How We Collect Data</h2>
      <p>We gather information through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Forms you fill out (contact forms, sign-ups)</li>
        <li>Automated tracking tools (cookies, analytics)</li>
        <li>Third-party services (e.g., payment processors)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>4. Why We Collect Data</h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about updates and offers</li>
        <li>Ensure legal compliance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>5. Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        We implement security measures to protect your data, including
        encryption, secure servers, and limited access protocols.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>6. Sharing Data with Third Parties</h2>
      <p>
        We may share your data with trusted third parties, such as payment
        processors and analytics providers, only as necessary to provide our
        services.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request corrections or deletions of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>8. International Data Transfers</h2>
      <p>
        If your data is transferred outside your country, we will take steps to
        ensure it remains protected according to this policy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>9. Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
        posted on this page with an updated effective date.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
        at:
      </p>
      <p>Email: [Insert Email Address]</p>
      <p>Phone: [Insert Phone Number]</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .section {
    margin: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-family: "bungee";
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }
  .section p,
  .section li {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  strong{
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08rem;
  }

  @media (width < 40rem) {
    .section h2{
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section p, .section li{
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
